						               													<description>Blended is a party game where players take turns drawing cards from a deck and play the mini games presented in them to win and to earn money. The deck is made up of different types of games, some of them competitive, others cooperative and some just random, (like a roulette where you bet on the color of the next card).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game gets more interesting with the play cards that each player holds in their hands. with them, they can choose who to play with or against, and also they can attack, steal money and protect themselves from other players attacks.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The players in their turn will pick up a mini game, and using their own play cards, will choose who to play the game with or against. the winners get paid Blendollars.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The first player to get 25 Blendollars or be the last one with money is the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
